00:53:29.340 --> 00:53:34.340
in my life, in our church that we're a praying church?

00:53:34.340 --> 00:53:37.420
When's the last time we've been astonished

00:53:37.420 --> 00:53:42.420
because we've seen God do what only God can do?

00:53:43.420 --> 00:53:45.140
We said kind of like Hezekiah.

00:53:46.900 --> 00:53:50.300
Lord, here's what they've said.

00:53:50.300 --> 00:53:52.140
Laid out the letters before God.

00:53:54.260 --> 00:53:55.900
God, it's the truth.

00:53:55.900 --> 00:53:57.820
They've done everything that they said they've done

00:53:57.820 --> 00:54:01.340
to all the other nations but you're God.

00:54:03.260 --> 00:54:08.260
You're God and God worked because Hezekiah prayed.

00:54:08.260 --> 00:54:09.100
Let's pray together.

00:54:09.100 --> 00:54:10.140
Father, we love you.

00:54:11.020 --> 00:54:12.940
Thank you so much for loving us.

00:54:14.300 --> 00:54:16.100
I thank you for the privilege of prayer.

00:54:16.100 --> 00:54:18.500
I thank you for the power of prayer.

00:54:18.500 --> 00:54:22.460
I thank you that the early church was a praying church.

00:54:23.540 --> 00:54:27.340
Praying church is made up of praying people.

00:54:29.500 --> 00:54:31.740
God, I pray that we'd be a people of prayer.

00:54:32.980 --> 00:54:37.100
So often prayer is easy to talk about,

00:54:37.100 --> 00:54:40.540
it's easy to sing about, it's easy to preach about

00:54:42.260 --> 00:54:43.380
but praying is work.

00:54:45.020 --> 00:54:46.780
Distractions can abound.

00:54:48.140 --> 00:54:50.420
Busyness can distract us.

00:54:52.580 --> 00:54:55.260
God, I pray that you'd help us to be a praying people,

00:54:56.740 --> 00:54:58.100
a praying church.

00:54:59.020 --> 00:55:01.020
Would you have your will and way in the hearts and lives

00:55:01.020 --> 00:55:02.980
of those that are present this morning?

00:55:04.220 --> 00:55:06.460
God, do a work in our hearts.

00:55:06.500 --> 00:55:08.540
A work that would not soon be forgotten.

00:55:11.220 --> 00:55:13.620
A work that would bring forth fruits

00:55:15.340 --> 00:55:20.340
because God, prayer is our response to your ability

00:55:22.140 --> 00:55:24.140
and we know that you can do everything.

00:55:25.500 --> 00:55:28.140
There's nothing too hard for thee.

00:55:28.140 --> 00:55:29.660
We commit these moments to you.

00:55:29.660 --> 00:55:30.860
Pray that you'd have your will and way

00:55:30.860 --> 00:55:32.180
for it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:55:32.180 --> 00:55:33.380
Would you stand with me?

00:55:34.460 --> 00:55:36.260
I know we don't have the same kind of altar in here

00:55:37.100 --> 00:55:38.220
that we do in the other room

00:55:38.220 --> 00:55:41.540
but maybe this morning the Lord spoke into your heart

00:55:41.540 --> 00:55:43.980
through the preaching of his word,

00:55:43.980 --> 00:55:45.820
convicted you at some level.

00:55:46.780 --> 00:55:47.940
Kimberly's gonna play.

